snippet.title: Black The Fall
snippet.description:
Black The Fall  is an atmospheric side scroller that takes place in a decadent, industrial era. 
It’s inspired by our communist past and it features a world full of paranoia.

It combines stealth with puzzle solving and platformer elements.
